'''捍卫自由律师团'''（'''Lawyers for Liberty'''）是由一群[[马来西亚|马来西亚]]律师所组成的维权律师团队，旨在捍卫自由人权，推动司法改革，维护马来西亚国民权利。

这个律师团处理各种涉及马来西亚国民人权遭侵犯的课题，如警方滥权<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chinapress.com.my/20140928/%E6%8D%8D%E8%A1%9B%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E5%9C%98%E8%AD%A6%E5%BA%A6%E6%8F%90%E6%8E%A7%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%88%E4%BF%A1%E7%94%A8/|author=|title=捍衛自由律師團：警3度提控不守信用|publisher=中国报|date=2014-09-28|access-date=2015-12-01|archive-date=2017-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170908202208/http://www.chinapress.com.my/20140928/%e6%8d%8d%e8%a1%9b%e8%87%aa%e7%94%b1%e5%be%8b%e5%b8%ab%e5%9c%98%e8%ad%a6%e5%ba%a6%e6%8f%90%e6%8e%a7%e4%b8%8d%e5%ae%88%e4%bf%a1%e7%94%a8/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.sinchew.com.my/node/441383?tid=1|author=|title=警方捕逾百音樂會出席者‧捍衛自由律師團斥濫權|publisher=星洲日报|date=2015-09-02|access-date=2015-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208062734/http://news.sinchew.com.my/node/441383?tid=1|archive-date=2015-12-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>、嫌犯在扣留所死亡或遭到虐待案件<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.sinchew.com.my/node/431005?tid=1|author=|title=人權委會等展開聯合運動‧促政府簽反酷刑公約|publisher=星洲日报|date=2015-06-26|access-date=2015-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208054306/http://news.sinchew.com.my/node/431005?tid=1|archive-date=2015-12-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.malaysiakini.com/news/201654|author=|title=难忍疲劳盘问及辣椒涂私处，伊拉克扣留者多次试图自杀|publisher=当今大马|date=2012-06-22|access-date=2015-12-01|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304112037/http://www.malaysiakini.com/news/201654|dead-url=no}}</ref>、警方不合程序开枪射杀嫌犯案件<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.orientaldaily.com.my/nation/gn39553|author=|title=15岁少年被警员鎗杀，捍卫自由律师团要求司法检討|publisher=东方日报|date=2013-12-23|access-date=2015-12-01|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305014316/http://www.orientaldaily.com.my/nation/gn39553|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.malaysiakini.com/news/148354|author=|title=又有16岁少年被控袭警遭击毙，人权律师批警方重演阿米奴案|publisher=当今大马|date=2010-11-16|access-date=2015-12-01|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304193241/http://www.malaysiakini.com/news/148354|dead-url=no}}</ref>、政治异议分子遭执法官员逮捕和起诉案件，为这些案件中的当事人或当事人家属提供法律援助。

过去曾得到捍卫自由律师团支援的有社运组织成员、学运领袖、马来西亚在野党领袖、政治漫画家、异议部落客、国外政治难民等等。<ref name="#1">{{en}}{{cite web|url= http://www.lawyersforliberty.org/about/|author= |title= About Us|publisher= |date= |access-date= 2015-11-30|archive-date= 2012-02-14|archive-url= https://www.webcitation.org/65SJT5kaQ?url=http://www.lawyersforliberty.org/about/|dead-url= no}}</ref>

==关注课题==

捍卫自由律师团积极投入公民教育工作，通过各种管道增进国民的人权常识。<ref name="#1"/>他们高度关注马来西亚国内的各种司法课题，监督司法改革进程，也参与推动废除死刑<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.malaysiakini.com/news/139673|author=郭史光庆|title=律师向新国上书促废除死刑，死者父亲倾家荡产为儿申冤|publisher=当今大马|date=2010-08-10|access-date=2015-11-30|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305011017/http://www.malaysiakini.com/news/139673|dead-url=no}}</ref>、捍卫媒体自由<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.sinchew.com.my/node/435361|author=|title=捍卫自由律师团促内政部撤回停刊决定|publisher=星洲日报|date=2015-07-25|access-date=2015-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208063931/http://news.sinchew.com.my/node/435361|archive-date=2015-12-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>、维护动物权利<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.sinchew.com.my/node/191606#sthash.8niA7fkg.dpuf|author=|title=大马虐狗短片犯众怒|publisher=星洲日报|date=2011-01-27|access-date=2015-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305133459/http://news.sinchew.com.my/node/191606#sthash.8niA7fkg.dpuf|archive-date=2016-03-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>等运动。

